  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 7th level, you gain an additional Cursed Weapon.</p><p> Thia Cursed weapon becomes unbreakable, is Superior in quality, and when you make an attack with it, you may spend 5 Chakra.</p><p> On a hit, the target must make a Constitution saving throw vs Your Taijutsu Save DC.</p><p> On a failed save, they gain the Cursed Condition.</p><p> Additionally, you may learn an additional taijutsu/weapon stance.</p><p> You may gain the benefits of two stances at once.</p><p> Finally, select one adversary trait of C-rank or lower, this is applied to this weapon and you gain its benefits while you wield it.</p><p> This cannot be a iconic trait.</p><p> Creatures of a different class/subclass do not gain the benefits of this trait.</p><p></p>",
